{"tid":1775532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 低調癱瘓地鐵 膠水黐車門","createTime":"2019-12-09T02:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T02:44:22.000Z","uid":293896,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"343e84fa0330954fbaebe17a33fff74fbb54ea43","tid":1775532,"uid":293896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"事先聲明: 本人爱蝈爱黨鉄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑衣暴徒千祈唔好黐黨鉄車門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其高調頂住車門 dum野落路軌 比班藍屍影相/阻鳩住晒/鬧 不如低調係人多嘅時候用快乾超能膠黐實度門 即刻廢左個車廂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者低調咁滴d膠 然後用腳掃或者等佢慢慢滲d膠入條門軌度 硬左就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以做到無人見到 不過要有人幫手<br />\n1) 右臂挨喺車門中間 左手玩電話<br />\n2) 有fd企你前同後玩電話 (即係人牆遮視線)<br />\n3) 右手係褲袋攞支膠出嚟做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係只不過黐住度門 唔係幫人罷工 不過同請閘機食茄汁一樣 目的係增加黨鐵營運成本<br />\n<br />\ncons: <br />\n1) 當然黨鉄有cctv 好撚可疑<br />\n2) 用膠水會有陣味會聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3) 道門可能夠大力扯得爛d膠/未乾得切<br />\n<br />\n可行性?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可行你老味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千祈唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510a2a3b81850d404fe3af05eb205566a11f955e","tid":1775532,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5282368260d4c417834178d8dd41da24d83c1593","tid":1775532,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"6c17944d0c02754ffbd269285db9179e563890d3","tid":1775532,"uid":187082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"343e84fa0330954fbaebe17a33fff74fbb54ea43","tid":1775532,"uid":29